        "擦油"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "擦"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "摩，搓，用手反复揉搓",
      "examples": [
        "摩拳擦掌",
        "擦澡"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "擦"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "贴近，靠近而不接触或仅轻微接触",
      "examples": [
